thread.title: Kitten stuck between semi-truck’s wheels rescued, officials say

author: @wcjb20
title: Kitten stuck between semi-truck’s wheels rescued, officials say
text:
A kitten was rescued from a semi's wheel well after a commercial driver noticed it. (SOURCE: Ohio State Highway Patrol) By Andrew McMunn Published: Jun. 20, 2024 at 6:12 PM EDT | Updated: 5 hours ago Email This Link
Share on Facebook
Share on X (formerly Twitter)
Share on Pinterest
Share on LinkedIn
PORTAGE COUNTY, Ohio (Gray News) – A kitten was rescued after he found himself stuck in a semi-truck’s wheel well.
According to the Ohio State Highway Patrol , the rescue took place on May 14.
A commercial truck driver had noticed the kitten between the tires of his semi during a pre-trip inspection on the Ohio Turnpike in Portage County.
The state patrol said “purrfect” teamwork was used to save the kitten from its entrapment.
The kitten was then turned unharmed into the hands of the Portage Animal Protective League.
